
Title:
TalentLens AI

AI-Powered Skill Discovery and Opportunity Matching Platform


---

1. Project Overview

TalentLens AI is an intelligent platform designed to identify, analyze, and utilize the hidden skills of students. Many students possess valuable technical and non-technical skills, but these skills often remain unnoticed by institutions, faculty members, and recruiters. As a result, students miss opportunities while organizations struggle to find suitable candidates.

The proposed system uses Artificial Intelligence to extract skills from resumes, certifications, and project experiences. Based on the identified skills, the platform recommends suitable projects, internships, hackathons, research activities, and competitions.

The platform helps institutions make better use of student talent while ensuring that students receive opportunities that match their abilities and interests.


---

2. Problem Statement

Educational institutions often face difficulties in identifying and utilizing the hidden skills of students. Traditional methods rely on academic scores and manual evaluation, which do not accurately represent a student's complete skill set.

As a result:

Talented students remain unnoticed.

Opportunities are not allocated efficiently.

Teams are formed without considering actual skills.

Students miss projects, internships, and competitions that match their capabilities.


There is a need for an intelligent system that can automatically discover student skills and match them with relevant opportunities.


---

3. Proposed Solution

TalentLens AI provides an AI-driven platform that:

Collects student profiles and resumes.

Extracts skills using Artificial Intelligence.

Stores and organizes skill information.

Matches students with suitable opportunities.

Recommends projects, internships, hackathons, and research activities.

Assists faculty members in identifying suitable candidates for academic and research work.


The system acts as a bridge between talent and opportunity.


---

